The `Navbar` component is included in the `Header` area, which will span the full width of the page at the top. This is aligned with the usual navigation bar concept.

In the `ImagesPage` component, you include both the image grid and a control panel, which is situated to the side of the content:

```jsx
// src/pages/ImagesPage/index.jsx
import React from 'react';
import { Layout } from 'antd';
import ImageGrid from '../../components/ImageGrid';
import ImageActionBar from '../../components/ImageActionBar';
import ControlPanel from '../../components/ControlPanel';

const { Content, Sider } = Layout;

