Remember to apply appropriate CSS to achieve the styling you desire, such as making the header stick to the top or adjusting the padding and margin around different layout areas. With Ant Design's `Layout` component, you have flexibility in structuring these components, and you can also customize the theme and appearance using CSS or LESS.

