This ensures that the navigation `Sider` takes up the full height of the page on the left side, and the `Content` area displays the page-specific content on the right.

I hope this clears up the confusion and aligns with your desired layout. Adjust the style and dimensions as necessary to achieve the exact look and feel you want for your application.

